kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc4=Base energy usage: §b1920§7 EU/t
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc5=Supports §dperfect OC!
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc6=Has a minimum recipe time of 20 ticks, further overclocks multiply outputs by 4x
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc7=Recipe time is based on mob health
