kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc11=Enable Weapon Cycling to pull a weapon from input when the current one breaks or is moved to an output
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc12=§cEnchanting the spikes inside the structure does nothing!
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc13=If the mob spawns §cinfernal§7, it will drain 8 times more power!
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc14=You can prevent §cinfernal§7 spawns by shift clicking with a screwdriver
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc15=Mobs who are always §cinfernal§7 will ignore this factor
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc16=You can enable ritual mode with a screwdriver
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc17=When in ritual mode, can link to above Well of Suffering rituals
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc18=The Ritual must be built directly centered above the machine
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc19=When linked, mobs will start to buffer and die very slowly, providing blood to the linked altar
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc20=You can disable mob animation with a soldering iron
kubatech.multiblock.ExtremeEntityCrusher.desc21=You can enable batch mode with wire cutters. Providing §916x Time, Output, Weapon Damage
